Package exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ClashingRegisteredIndexNumberException
    This is a class that extends Exception which is thrown when there is a clash between registered index numbers and the index number a student is currently trying to register.
    ClashingWaitListedIndexNumberException
    This is a class that extends Exception which is thrown when there is a clash between waitlisted index numbers and the index number a student is currently trying to register.
    CourseInWaitListException
    This is a class that extends Exception which is thrown when the course the student is trying to register for is already in wait-list.
    CourseRegisteredException
    This is a class that extends Exception which is thrown when the course the student is trying to register for is already registered for them.
    InvalidAccessTimeException
    This is a class that extends Exception which is thrown when the course the student is trying to access STARS Application past their end date and time.
    InvalidLessonTypeException
    This is a class that extends Exception which is thrown when the lesson type is anything other than LAB, LECTURE or TUTORIAL.
    InvalidNewMaxException
    This is a class that extends Exception which is thrown when the maximum vacancy for a particular Index Number of a particular Course is less than 1 or contains special characters.
    MaxAuExceededException
    This is a class that extends Exception which is thrown when the student attempts to register a course that will cause them to break their maximum vacancy ceiling.
    NoVacancyException
    This is a class that extends Exception which is thrown when there is no vacancy in the particular Index Number of a particular Course.
    NoVacancySwapException
    This is a class that extends Exception which is thrown when there is no vacancy in the particular Index Number of a particular Course that the student is trying to swap their own registered Index Number with.
    PeerClashingRegisteredIndexNumberException
    This is a class that extends Exception which is thrown when the timetable of the registered Index Number of peer clashes with the student's own index number's timetable.
    PeerClashingWaitListedIndexNumberException
    This is a class that extends Exception which is thrown when the timetable of the waitlisted Index Number of peer clashes with the student's own index number's timetable.
    SameIndexNumberSwapException
    This is a class that extends Exception which is thrown when the student attempts to swap Index Number with the same Index Number from the same Course.
    WrongAccessPeriodException
    This is a class that extends Exception which is thrown when the course the student is trying to access STARS Application outside of their access period.
    WrongLoginInfoException
    This is a class that extends Exception which is thrown when the LoginInfo is inaccurate.
